intel-arc-a580-review-a-new-budget-contender&quot;>;作为汤姆的硬件...&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/10/23911902/intel-arc -a580-announcement-performance-price-nvidia-amd&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/10/23911902/intel-arc-a580-announcement-performance-price-nvidia-amd" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/10/23911902/intel-arc-a580-announcement-performance-price-nvidia-amd</id><author><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-10T18:54:34-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-10T18:54:34-04:00</updated><title>亚马逊 10 月 Prime Day 活动可享受 Apple 最佳优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;苹果第二代 AirPods Pro 的女性头像侧面照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/t_enweqg84BVnbmgObNVVrejL2k=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72740712/226285_AIRPODS_PRO_2_cwelch_0002 .0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;即使是配备 USB-C 的更新版第二代 AirPods Pro 现已开始销售。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;1696954159.110949&quot;>;&lt;em>;亚马逊秋季 Prime Day 活动正在进行中。如需了解我们推荐的所有类别的更多优惠，请查看我们的 &lt;/em>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23905078/amazon-october-prime-day-best-deals-tech-gadgets-2023 &quot;>;&lt;em>;这里有完整的综述&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;&lt;em>;。&lt;/em>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;XzPHSJ&quot;>;苹果很少给自己的产品打折，所以如果你想获得一个购买一对 AirPods 或 MacBook 很划算，最好将目光投向亚马逊等第三方。但是，如果您错过了我们在第一个 Prime Day 期间看到的 Apple 折扣，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23903764/amazon-october-prime-day-deals-tips-news-guide -2023&quot;>;亚马逊 10 月 Prime Day 活动&lt;/a>;让其中一些人回归。我们再次看到 Apple Watch、平板电脑甚至新款 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Generation-Cancelling-Transparency-Personalized/dp/B0CHWRXH8B/?tag= theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;配备 USB-C 的第二代 AirPods Pro&lt;/a>;，不到一个月前推出。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;247U