lorado-right-to-repair-law- Farmers-farming-equipment&quot;>;科罗拉多州&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/5/24/23736326/minnesota-right-to-repair-laws-passed- electronics -free-documentation&quot;>;明尼苏达州&lt;/a>;，比它的一些前任更加严厉。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>; &lt;aside id=&quot;wAGPac&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;修复权：所有最新新闻和更新&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/5/28/23738770/right-to-修复更新法律&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;div id=&quot;OfrnJQ&quot;>; &lt;blockquote class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot;>; &lt;p lang=&quot;en&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;>;打破！ &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/CAgovernor?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot;>;@CAGovernor&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/GavinNewsom?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot;>; @GavinNewsom&lt;/a>; 刚刚为 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/hashtag/SB244?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot;>;#SB244&lt;/a>; 签名://twitter.com/hashtag/RightToRepair?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot;>;#RightToRepair&lt;/a>;！获得修复产品所需的东西对于消费者和地球来说都是双赢，而且这是有道理的。感谢 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/SenSusanEggman?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot;>;@SenSusanEggman&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/CALPIRG?ref_src =twsrc%5Etfw&quot;>;@CALPIRG&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/iFixit?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot;>;@iFixit&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter .com/cawrecycles?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot;>;@cawrecycles&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/RepairCoalition?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot;>;@...&lt;/a>;&lt;/ p>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;/div>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23910066/right-to-repair-law-newsom-california-sb-244&quot; >;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23910066/right-to-repair-law-newsom-california-sb-244" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> htt